How to add a Quiz? How to see created Quizzes? Can I edit the Created Quiz problems? I am a Quiz Participant. How to Get the Quiz Id? How to Join a Quiz? I am a Quiz Participant. Can I see my Quiz Results? How to see the Leaderboard of a created Quiz? How to see marks of my past attended Quizzes? Privacy Do you like Our App? What can I do if I see something unusual happening in the App?
Go to the Quiz section using the navigation bar. You can click on New Quiz to create a quiz. Then You have to add the Quiz details (Name of the Quiz, Start Date, Start Time, and Duration). Click the Next button and you will redirect to a page to add Questions. After adding the Question You have to provide the fours answers and the correct answer. By Clicking Add To List, You will be able to add previous question to the list and add another Question. After adding 1 or more Questions, You can create the Quiz by Clicking Finish Button.After successful submission, you will get a pop-up message.You can also copy the quiz id from here and share it with the quiz participants Go to Home Section using the Navigation bar. You can click Schedule to see your created Quizzes. In the Schedule section you can see your created Quizzes.After clicking one of the Quizzes you will be able to update or delete the Corresponding Quiz problems.You can also add new Questions here Quiz Creator must share the quiz id with his participants.He/she will copy the quiz id after creating the Quiz and share it with you. Go to Quiz Section using the Navigation bar. You can click on Join to join a quiz. After the quiz starting time, You have to enter a correct quiz id to join a quiz. After Submitted the answered Quiz you will be able to see your results. Only the Quiz Creator can see the Leaderboard of his created Quizzes.He/she can go to the Leaderboard section using the navigation bar to see the leaderboards of each quiz. Go to Home Section using the navigation bar. You can click on Past Quizzes to see your past attended Quizzes. It will show the quiz name, date, time, and marks of each quiz. Do not forget to rate Quiz Me on PlayStore 100% private. No personal data collection. No data sharing with third parties. Be kind to tell the problem to us using the play store review section.
